long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Where you can get very useful links to different Chess sites and Chess games online.
 
The search functionalities integrated within the extension are provided by Microsoft Bing;

By installing the "Chess Start" extension, you agree to the 
Terms of Service (https://chess-start.com/terms.html) and 
Privacy Policy. (https://chess-start.com/privacy.html)


This extension will not alter any settings related to your default browser search.

Chess Start is presented by Manga Pulse Ltd.
